<promed@promedmail.org>

[WPV1 circulation continues in Pakistan. These 3 cases are not as yet included in the weekly global update (see section [2] below) and when added will raise the global tally of WPV1 associated polio to 88 cases during 2019.

Of note, a prior case mentioned in Punjab has not as yet been officially confirmed and may have well been a suspected case pending laboratory results.

A good map of Pakistan showing districts and provinces can be found at https://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/pak215_pakistan_districts_v5_a0_20181203.pdf. - Mod.MPP]

