[Circulation of both WPVs and cVDPVs continues as seen with newly confirmed cases in Pakistan (WPV1), DR Congo (cVDPV2), Ghana (cVDPV2) and the Philippines (cVDPV2). In addition, environmental samples were positive in Pakistan (WPV1 - widespread), Ghana (cVDPV2 around the capital region and the north) and the Philippines (cVDPV2 in the southern region and cVDPV1 around the metro Manila region).

The good news is that no new countries have joined the list of countries with identified poliovirus circulation. The not so good news is that it's clear there is significant circulation of cVDPVs in Ghana and the Philippines, both countries that had been polio free for 19 years.

